Dog Daddy doesn’t refuse to help any dog, no matter how impossible them appear.
“My dog is too aggressive , no one can ever train him”
So as long as the owners are willing, Dog Daddy is willing to teach them what they need.
Being that he was misunderstood his whole life Dog Daddy can easily relate to these dogs:
Thousands of dogs helped and thousands more currently signed up for upcoming classes worldwide.
All the videos are the results of just their first training session. The owners are left with homework and proper tools to succeed with their dogs after spending hours training with Dog Daddy.
